# Salon Booking System — 8-Slide Presentation

---

## Slide 1: Project Overview

**Title:** Salon Booking System — Full-Stack Web Application

**Tagline:** *Bridging salon owners and customers through seamless digital appointment management.*

**Problem Statement:**

- 📌 Manual salon scheduling is error-prone and time-consuming
- 📌 No real-time slot visibility for customers
- 📌 Owners lack tooling to manage bookings, services & notifications centrally

**Solution:**

- ✅ Browser-based platform for two distinct user roles
- ✅ Real-time slot availability with a 10-minute booking hold
- ✅ Automated cron-driven lifecycle management of appointments

**Demo Credentials:**

| Role | Email | Password |
|---|---|---|
| Owner | <owner@salon.com> | Owner@123 |
| Customer | <customer@example.com> | Customer@123 |

