## Slide 2: Key Features & User Flows

**Title:** What Can Users Do?

| Salon Owner | Customer |
|---|---|
| Register & configure salon profile | Browse & search all salons |
| Set working hours, day off & lunch break | View services, ratings & reviews |
| Add / remove services with pricing | Check live available time slots |
| Confirm / reject incoming bookings | Book one or more consecutive slots |
| Receive email/SMS notifications | Confirm booking within 10-min hold |
| View full booking history | Cancel bookings & submit reviews |

**System Automation (Cron Jobs):**

```
┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  releaseAbandonedSlots  →  free slots after 10-min hold   │
│  autoConfirmBookings    →  auto-confirm eligible bookings  │
│  markCompleted          →  close past appointments        │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

