## Slide 6: API Design

**Title:** REST API Surface

### Auth — `/api/auth` (Public)

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/register` | Register new user (owner or customer) |
| POST | `/login` | Authenticate & create session |
| POST | `/logout` | Destroy session |
| GET | `/me` | Get current session user |
| POST | `/reset-password` | Reset via email + last 4 digits of phone |

### Owner — `/api/owner` *(owner role required)*

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET/PUT | `/profile` | View or update salon profile |
| PUT | `/schedule` | Update working hours & lunch break |
| GET/POST | `/services` | List or add services |
| DELETE | `/services/:id` | Remove a service |
| GET | `/bookings` | View all incoming bookings |
| PUT | `/bookings/:id/confirm` | Confirm a booking |
| PUT | `/bookings/:id/reject` | Reject a booking |

### Customer — `/api/customer` *(customer role required)*

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/owners` | Browse all registered salons |
| GET | `/owners/:id` | Salon detail + services + rating |
| GET | `/owners/:id/slots` | Available slots for a date |
| GET/POST | `/bookings` | List or create bookings |
| PUT | `/bookings/:id/confirm` | Confirm within 10-min hold |
| PUT | `/bookings/:id/cancel` | Cancel a booking |
| POST | `/reviews` | Submit rating & review |

### Public

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/services` | Global services catalogue |
| GET | `/api/health` | Server + DB health check |

